{"tid":2011763,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[新聞刺針] 創科局資助逾400萬  長者實測八段錦興趣不大  開發程式手動篩圖耗時費力","createTime":"2020-05-11T08:25:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-11T15:00:38.000Z","uid":37757,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"3e893cadf97722e3c990a99f7ca2bce400aa4b2b","tid":2011763,"uid":37757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T08:25:21.000Z","msg":"政府創科生活基金，資助手機App陸續面世，其中兩款標榜人工智能的APP，包括「智能八段錦」及由亞洲糖尿病基金會開發、賣點是以AI識別食物營養成份「Citybite」，均獲得超過400萬元資助。<br />\n<br />\n《新聞刺針》找來用家及手機遊戲開發公司實測兩款App，由他們評價是否物有所值。<br />\n<br />\nsource : <br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/24997\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F24997&d=jhMTXyFjUfd7nN31cC%2BnyYaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=9860ec13\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F24997&h=518a923d\" target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/24997</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/posts/1444181052440625\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ficablenews%2Fposts%2F1444181052440625&d=jhMTXyFjUfd7nN31cC%2BnyYaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=fdbbb78b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/posts/1444181052440625</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n１) 兩個APP均由同一間公司開發，超過４００萬資助<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JrNraC8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJrNraC8.jpg&h=ec96c7e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KRgSQC9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKRgSQC9.jpg&h=a4345ebe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n２) 八段錦APP長者意見皆為負面<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8vDU3X3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8vDU3X3.jpg&h=aca03e21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3V488pK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3V488pK.jpg&h=5190459b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YjNFZwq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYjNFZwq.jpg&h=55eea2ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3) 完全沒有跟指令也獲四星高分<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kYxntpN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkYxntpN.jpg&h=0bb64159&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4) 同為項目主任的申請人稱使用平板電腦比較好<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tqONEwq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtqONEwq.jpg&h=8b7dc419&s={SIZE}\" />   <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iiqTz4Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiiqTz4Q.jpg&h=82e100ed&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n5) 業界同行項目估算 (八段錦)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ftxZvDb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FftxZvDb.jpg&h=095c14ed&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n6) 另一APP CITYBITE<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eufTz86.jpg\" data-thumbn